Package: enotebook
Title: R Client for ENotebook Electronic Lab Notebook
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("ENotebook", "Team", , "support@enotebook.local", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tidyverse-friendly functions for interacting with the
    ENotebook Electronic Lab Notebook API. Scientists can programmatically
    extract experimental data, perform analysis in R, and push results back
    to the ELN. Supports both REST and GraphQL APIs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
